-------------------------------------
deathrun_tp_dissolution
-------------------------------------
This is a deathrun map. 

The objective is for the CTs to get to the end of the map without dying from the traps which are operated by the Ts. When you win you get a shotgun to blow off the Ts' heads.
-------------------------------------
Spawns
CT = 27 spawns (most deathrun servers are 18 slots with 3 Ts and the rest CT)
T = 3 spawns
-------------------------------------
Credits
Map made by Loller Dan
Inspired by Corn Ibulus 
-------------------------------------
There is 1 easter egg. Happy hunting.
Tested on 66 tic only
-------------------------------------
